{"id": 890, "genre": 1001, "title": "你出国自助游时在国外遇到过什么麻烦？", "description": "“外？你好？Hello？我被大象踩了……”（题图来自：Jon Juarez）", "record_count": 2730, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160702183542BP2tRd5Jw81uKzng.jpeg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-03-23T10:58:29Z", "options": [{"id": 60930, "content": "在清迈夜市想买东西却没有现金和银联卡，于是搭讪了一对中国情侣，用支付宝现场套现。", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 530088}, {"id": 60931, "content": "在时代广场跨年，到处被封路，地铁口就在对面，警察叔叔就是不让过马路", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 479392}, {"id": 79876, "content": "荒山野岭迷路", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 614458}, {"id": 60934, "content": "歧视", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 114917}, {"id": 60937, "content": "?", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 529547}, {"id": 60938, "content": "哈哈哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 530141}, {"id": 60941, "content": "和同胞讲英语", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 530147}, {"id": 60942, "content": "有点多，去好莱坞坐公交去的，回得时候公交点等公交直接周日车不经过那里了，然后大晚上几个女孩儿超级害怕……还有刚去等Peterpan一下子等了4小时", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 530156}, {"id": 60943, "content": "无法沟通", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 459648}, {"id": 61200, "content": "从曼谷到清迈的之后遇到一个欧美男屌丝，名字叫Dan ，聊了一路，还了得特好！到站后，我先去了青旅，结果发现这货拿着啤酒躺在沙发上百无聊赖，一问你咋在这？他说他是青旅老板。之后基本上是老板带我玩一路，攀岩啊，蹦极啊，还免房钱。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 403067}, {"id": 60945, "content": "没有钱出去…", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 530159}, {"id": 60946, "content": "在la机场附近alamo租车 被前台白人老头子推销各种车险我一一拒绝就被他说中国人只知道把钱放钱包里不知道花 我就呵呵了自驾完之后去还车跟他们门店manager argue了两个小时", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 530158}, {"id": 61202, "content": "tt", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 532084}, {"id": 61458, "content": "不想要热狗夹菜的我那下意识地用“Yes!”回复对方的“No lettuce？”的中式语法把赛百味的英国小哥弄得一脸懵逼。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 461690}, {"id": 60948, "content": "按谷歌地图提供的路线没找到酒店", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 345450}, {"id": 60949, "content": "在印度共产主义强制我把其他的游客钱给了！并且不找零", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 520683}, {"id": 60951, "content": "从荷兰去柏林，却偏偏德国铁路大罢工", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 526947}, {"id": 60953, "content": "被拉客司机黑   跟着我们不让我们走   一定要那一百块钱，为此恨屋及乌", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 86649}, {"id": 60954, "content": "越南人满脸笑容地坑你（仅限我遇到的那些）", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 365170}, {"id": 60955, "content": "没去过", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 530198}, {"id": 60956, "content": "和当地人共通的语言只有英语，但是交流后才发现原来我们说的英语也是不同的呀", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 522720}, {"id": 60957, "content": "把护照弄丢了……算吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 485781}, {"id": 61982, "content": "日本人看见我都用韩语跟我讲话 韩国人看见我都用日语跟我讲话 excuse me？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 536786}, {"id": 60959, "content": "外语张不开嘴，常常处于交流恐惧状态中。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 482218}, {"id": 60960, "content": "同一条路不认路 被当地人指来指去走了三次 简直了", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 337845}, {"id": 60962, "content": "被当地交警吭了钱……", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 410187}, {"id": 63266, "content": "坐了一个通宵飞机到了国外，TM这什么鸟地方，居然没有卖打火机的?", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 542164}, {"id": 60963, "content": "由于过香港海关人太多，错过香港快运廉航的最后check in时间..欲哭无泪！！！重新买机票飞东京...", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 530227}, {"id": 60965, "content": "司机只会讲阿拉伯语……", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 26306}, {"id": 60966, "content": "没钱", "image": "img/option/option/20160606144958x9UHwVBKgNPYDu8T.jpg", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 530312}, {"id": 60967, "content": "迷路", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 530312}, {"id": 60968, "content": "遇到海关敲诈贿赂，和他们领导沟通后换了一个窗口，那个人骂F开头的。勇敢回骂了回去", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 530316}, {"id": 60969, "content": "店家不懂英文，点吃的全靠瞎蒙。后来是叫邻座的日本女生帮忙翻译，无奈双方英文都烂，最后就看那个女生吃的啥就点啥", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 530306}, {"id": 60970, "content": "酒店机票下一秒都可以买好，但你妹没有签证，去屁啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 153428}, {"id": 61226, "content": "突然发现没零钱给小费", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 532173}, {"id": 60972, "content": "日语着急，在秋叶原问路用英文对方听到转头就走……?", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 459273}, {"id": 60973, "content": "国家不让去算吗", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 487739}, {"id": 60974, "content": "天天吃面包，已吃哭……", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 530132}, {"id": 60975, "content": "考虑应该给多少小费的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 165309}, {"id": 60976, "content": "被美国海关的傻叉系统误认为是通缉犯?，还要是60%相似??", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 525892}, {"id": 60977, "content": "找不到路啊啊啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 521525}, {"id": 60978, "content": "！！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 530375}, {"id": 60979, "content": "被说这是单行道，不准逆行。问题是你国人都在逆行。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 530389}, {"id": 60980, "content": "遇到大象拉的屎", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 513678}, {"id": 60981, "content": "还好呀", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 524425}, {"id": 61237, "content": "泰国落地签结果打印的机票坏掉了，海关不认！ 并且是在晚上十点，需要去另一个机场转机", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 532403}, {"id": 60982, "content": "钱包丟了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 448640}, {"id": 60985, "content": "几乎所有外国人都任性的认为我是韩国人", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 530509}, {"id": 60988, "content": "和逛街狂魔（♂）和爱妻狂魔逛日本银座 在咖啡厅睡了一上午", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 493335}, {"id": 60992, "content": "办了4个g的流量卡，结果只能用3天", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 504324}]}